metadata.name: On the streets of a small village
metadata.description:
twenty was driving an electric tricycle full of goods.



The young man, named Wang Xian, is one of the few college students in the village.



After graduating from university, Wang Xian stayed in the big city where he studied and had a stable job. The salary and working environment were excellent.



And, with her own efforts, Wang Xian was able to buy an apartment in that big city, with a down payment, of course.
